{"tid":351241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼「巴斯光年星際歷險」月底講拜拜","createTime":"2017-08-08T00:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T02:24:38.000Z","uid":51051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de05e8c891b4ae759bdd2c9943064b7428eee2cf","tid":351241,"uid":51051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:16:15.000Z","msg":"香港迪士尼樂園正進行擴建計劃籌備工作，其中明日世界園區的遊樂設施「巴斯光年星際歷險」將營業至本月31日後關閉，之後進行改裝工程變身以 Marvel 超級英雄為主題的互動射擊遊樂設施。<br />\n<br />\n樂園由8月8日起至8月31日，會安排巴斯光年現身主題區「明日世界」內「巴斯光年星際歷險」入口附近與市民合照，巴斯光年下月起會歸隊回到「反斗奇兵大本營」會眾。另外迪士尼亦特別推出相關主題貼紙在「明日世界」免費派給賓客收藏，同時有系列商品推出。「奇妙處處通」會員由8月9日起可親身到樂園內的「奇妙處處通」會員服務中心出示有效會員卡，即可獲贈「巴斯光年星際歷險」紀念特刊一本，數量有限，送完即止。<br />\n<br />\n巴斯光年星際歷險是迪士尼建園以來的恆常設施，乘客可駕駛太空巡邏車以雷射槍射擊邪惡的索克天王奪取高分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57052271&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57052271%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170807&d=Q8kexwpyODa3W3WSAApUUv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4d1eb2ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57052271%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170807&h=33d50ce9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57052271&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170807</a><br />\n<br />\n次次去迪士尼都會玩兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5e5de15ff6ad1ef8a0ae3ab8b795a60ffdbb42","tid":351241,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1e5ec6635671763e18047241435f9ad4b338d4","tid":351241,"uid":51051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blo